'desc': [u'

Farlin Fish Nail Clipper Price: Rs.297

Infant’s nails are soft but they still have to be trimmed to avoid dirt accumulation and to prevent the child from hurting himself. The Safety Scissors or the Fish Nail Clipper from Farlin is an adorable nail trimmer that comes in the shape of a fish. This Nail Clipper has a special design that allows you to collect the nails as you clip them. This feature will help you in preventing clipped nails getting shattered all over the place. There is a nail buff at the bottom of this Farlin Nail Clipper with which you can easily and effectively polish the rough edges of the nails. Make sure you buff the nails to prevent sharp and rough edges that can hurt your bundle of joy.

This Farlin Fish Nail Clipper comes with an anti-skid design that will keep the clipper firmly in your hand without slipping. The plastic used on the body of this Nail Clipper from Farlin is non-toxic. The small blades used in this Nail clipper let you watch the nails clearly and hence reduces the chances of bruising your infant’s fingers.

Chicco Baby Feeding Set (Multicolor) Price: Rs.599

The Chicco Baby Feeding Set presents a practical solution to a mess-free meal. The feeding set has three parts that include a non-slip dish and a dish with a lid. The two baby dishes can be combined together to make one covered dish that makes the feeding set ideal for travel. The non-slip design ensures that the dish stays on the table and doesn’t land on the floor while your baby attempts to eat on her own. The two dishes can be used to store different foods without mixing together
column13:
or you could even use one dish to store food and the other for cutlery. The Chicco Feeding set is made from hygienic and durable material that keeps food hot. The 2-in-1 Chicco Baby Feeding Set is suitable for babies of 6 months of age and above and makes mealtime fun and manageable.

column12:
'desc': [u'

Chicco Clip Texture (Yellow) Price: Rs.349

The one thing that parents shudder at the sight of is when their babies happily pick up their soothers off the floor and put them straight into their mouths. The action happens so quickly and unassumingly that you are almost never able to stop them from doing it and it is followed by long cries and shouts of disapproval
column13:
from you of course. Chicco presents a simple solution to this problem with the Chicco Clip Texture. This cute clip-on texture has a soft textile ribbon or a chain that is connected to the soother. The clip-on texture can be clipped to your baby\u2019s clothes and even if the soother drops out of your baby\u2019s mouth the chains prevents the soother from dropping on the floor and lets it dangle at a safe height from the floor.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis simple Chicco soother with chain prevents dirt and germs collecting on the soother and ensures better hygiene for your baby. Furthermore
column14:
you don\u2019t have to go hunting for the soother because it remains in the same place it was clipped on even after your baby sets out for their daily adventures.

\n
\n ']

column12:
'desc': [u'

Chicco 3-in-1 Bottle Brush (Blue) Price: Rs.475

All parents know that they have to keep their baby’s feeding bottles sparkling clean to ensure maximum hygiene for their little ones. But getting your hand all the way to bottom of the small baby bottles to clean out those milk remnants is almost an impossibility. Chicco understands how annoyingly frustrating this can be and has created the Chicco 3-in-1 Bottle Brush. This sleek and slender brush fits into any baby bottle of any design and helps you get to those difficult corners of the baby bottle. The nylon bristles help remove grease or milk residues effectively without damaging the smooth inner surface of the baby bottle.

The handle of 3-in-1 bottle brush from Chicco also has a special brush that effectively cleans teats and other feeding accessories. The handle also has a detachable pair of tongs that can be used to safely and hygienically remove baby bottles and feeding accessories after sterilization without touching them. This handy bottle brush from Chicco is a great time saver its other practical applications make is a useful cleaning device to own.

column12:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in Dark Price: Rs.175

Every new parent has been jolted out of bed in the middle of the night by the cries of their baby. As you get to your baby’s room
column13: half asleep and jostled by your baby\u2019s sharp crying
column14:
you find it almost impossible to locate your little one\u2019s pacifier. Farlin understands how parents can find these midnight tussles absolutely stressful and has created a very practical pacifier that can make life so much simpler. The Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in the Dark pacifier glows in the dark and allows you to find the pacifier in the jiffy and calm your baby in no time. The pacifier renders orthodontic advantages as well.

\r\n

\r\n\tMade from high quality silicone this firm and flexible pacifier promotes the natural development of your baby\u2019s palate
column15:
teeth and gums. The pacifier is soft and easy to suck and reduces pressure on the jaw during sucking. The bulb of the teat is designed to allow proper tongue placement during sucking. The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.

\n
\n ']

Chicco Zanza No Wipes (15 Pieces) Price: Rs.269

Wet wipes can be used for cleansing your tiny tot's skin after nappy change or even while travelling. The Chicco Zanza No Wipes are wet wipes that have been designed and created to keep your bundle of joy's skin protected. These Wet Wipes from Chicco have Citronella and Indian Lilac infused into them. The extracts of these plants have antibacterial and antiseptic properties that will help in safeguarding your baby's skin against such microorganisms. Indian Lilac also commonly known as Neem is good in treating various skin ailments and thus keeping the skin healthy.

The Zanza No Wipes from Chicco has a sweet fragrance that will linger on your and your little angel's skin after using this wipe. Your baby's skin will feel velvety soft and will have no graces of any dirt or excess oil after it is wiped clean by the Chicco Wet Wipes. These skin friendly Wet Wipes are suitable even for a newborn's fragile skin. Give your little darling the best cleansing experience with this Chicco Zanzo No Wipes that will soften and moisturize the skin.
